<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">
<head>
  <title>VOIDSECTOR | Leaderboard</title>
  <%- include('../partials/head') %>
  <style>
    .lb-wrap{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;}
    .lb-hero{display:flex;align-items:flex-end;justify-content:space-between;gap:16px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
    .lb-title{font-family:'Orbitron';color:#0ff;text-shadow:0 0 14px rgba(0,255,255,0.35);margin:0;font-size:30px;letter-spacing:1.2px;}
    .lb-sub{color:#9fb0c2;margin:8px 0 0;line-height:1.6;max-width:720px;}
    .lb-card{border:1px solid rgba(0,255,255,0.16);border-radius:16px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);padding:16px;box-shadow:0 12px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);}
    .lb-table{width:100%;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:0 10px;margin-top:14px;}
    .lb-row{background:rgba(0,0,0,0.28);border:1px solid rgba(0,255,255,0.14);}
    .lb-row td{padding:12px 14px;color:#d7e2ef;font-size:14px;}
    .lb-row td:first-child{border-top-left-radius:12px;border-bottom-left-radius:12px;}
    .lb-row td:last-child{border-top-right-radius:12px;border-bottom-right-radius:12px;text-align:right;color:#9ff;}
    .lb-head th{color:#8aa0b8;font-weight:600;font-size:12px;padding:0 14px;text-align:left;}
    .lb-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:8px 12px;border-radius:999px;border:1px solid rgba(255,0,255,0.20);background:rgba(255,0,255,0.06);color:#ffb3ff;font-size:12px;white-space:nowrap;}
    .lb-me{outline:2px solid rgba(255,0,255,0.45);box-shadow:0 0 0 6px rgba(255,0,255,0.10), 0 0 26px rgba(255,0,255,0.22);}
    .muted{color:#7f93a8;}
    .mono{font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;}
    .btn-mini{cursor:pointer;border-radius:999px;padding:9px 12px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.4px;
      border:1px solid rgba(0,255,255,0.22);background:rgba(0,255,255,0.08);color:#9ff;text-decoration:none;display:inline-flex;gap:8px;align-items:center;}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="background"></div>
  <%- include('../partials/topbar') %>

  <div class="container vs-page">
    <div class="lb-wrap">
      <div class="lb-hero">
        <div>
          <h1 class="lb-title">LEADERBOARD</h1>
          <p class="lb-sub">จัดอันดับคะแนนจาก <b style="color:#9ff;">ผลล่าสุด</b> ที่ทำ Quiz ของแต่ละบท (รวมทุกคอร์ส) — คะแนนจะอัปเดตทันทีหลัง Submit.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:center;">
          <span class="lb-badge">🏆 QUIZ RANKING</span>
          <a class="btn-mini" href="/learn/categories">🎓 Learn Hub</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="lb-card" style="margin-top:16px;">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
          <div>
            <div style="color:#0ff;font-family:'Orbitron';font-size:13px;letter-spacing:0.7px;">RANKINGS</div>
            <div class="muted" style="margin-top:6px;font-size:12px;">* ยิ่งทำ quiz เยอะ คะแนนรวม/เปอร์เซ็นต์จะยิ่งแม่น</div>
          </div>
          <button id="lbRefresh" class="btn-mini" type="button">🔄 Refresh</button>
        </div>

        <table class="lb-table">
          <thead class="lb-head">
            <tr>
              <th style="width:70px;">#</th>
              <th>Username</th>
              <th style="width:140px;">Score</th>
              <th style="width:120px;">%</th>
              <th style="width:220px;text-align:right;">Last Quiz</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody id="lbBody"></tbody>
        </table>

        <div id="lbEmpty" class="muted" style="display:none;padding:18px;text-align:center;">ยังไม่มีใครทำ quiz เลย — ไปทำคอร์สแล้วกลับมาดูอันดับได้ที่นี่ 🛰️</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script defer src="/js/leaderboard.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
